00:15:46.000 --> 00:15:50.000
it is subject to browser security restrictions.

00:15:50.000 --> 00:15:53.000
For example, it can't access files on disk,

00:15:53.000 --> 00:15:57.000
and it can't access a database on the network.

00:15:58.000 --> 00:16:01.000
Next, there's a lot of Python packages

00:16:01.000 --> 00:16:03.000
that can't yet run in the browser.

00:16:04.000 --> 00:16:07.000
